data.description: Coming Soon! Absolutely gorgeous two story has room for everything! Freshly painted throughout, the expansive open floor plan showcases fresh paint throughout, beautiful custom tile floors, separate living room, and spacious family room. At the heart of the home, a gourmet kitchen features ample cabinetry, granite countertops and backsplash, sleek stainless steel appliances, island, built-in desk, and pantry. Grand master suite has big walk-in closet, and luxurious bath with double vanity, soaking tub, and separate shower. Den/office and bonus loft for casual gatherings. Enjoy the private backyard from the covered patio or balcony in this fantastic neighborhood! For more information please email info@knock.com. There will not be a lockbox installed until listing preparation is complete and house is listed in MLS.
